		background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FFA500);
		border: none;
		border-radius: 14px;
		padding: 24px 20px;
	}

	.ny-fact-emoji {
		font-size: 28px;
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		line-height: 1;
	}

	.ny-fact-heading {
		font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
		font-size: 15px;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #1a1a2e;
		margin-bottom: 8px;
	}

	.ny-fact-text {
		font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
		font-size: 13px;
